<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.10">
<l>nākatti ṉaṇaiyāṉai naṉṉutalāḷ nayanturaicey</l>
<l>mēkattai vēṅkaṭakkōṉ viṭutūtil viṇṇappam</l>
<l>pōkattil vaḻuvāta putuvaiyarkōṉ kōtaitami</l>
<l>ḻākattu vaitturaippā ravaraṭiyā rākuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who, keeping [it] in their hearts, utter the Tamil [verses] of Kōtai—</l>
<l rend="indent">[the daughter of] the king of the Putuvai people,</l>
<l rend="indent">who did not swerve from the enjoyment [of God]—,</l>
<l>which is a request in [the form] a message sent [via] a cloud,</l>
<l rend="indent">that the woman with beautiful eyebrows spoke desiring the [Lord] on the snake bed</l>
<l rend="indent">will become His slaves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
